<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1260] The thrift THttpclient in c# client is not closing the connections when calling SendRequest</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1260</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When calling the server more than 16000 times, an exception is being thrown - &quot;An operation on a socket could not be performed because the system lacked sufficient buffer space or because a queue was full&quot; its because the stream is not being closed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12518607">THRIFT-1260</key>
